STATE OF FLORIDA, on the Relation of L. B. McLeod Construction Co., v. J. M. LEE, as Comptroller of the State of Florida. 22 So. (2nd) 808

June Term, 1945

July 20, 1945 En Banc J. Tom Watson, Attorney General and George M. Poweil, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent. PER CURIAM:

The motion to quash the alternative writ is denied on authority of State ex rel. Russell Badgett et al., v. J. M. Lee, Comptroller, filed this day.

*289CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BROWN, BUFORD, THOMAS, ADAMS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
